S.FORM: O Sow'hu Sra (Holam: Sra, ira ko Midipot to Sra) cacey kamoko'ay a tilifi ega i Taywan. Misanga' Pipahosoan to tilifi no Yen cu min ci ina to tilifi ega. Mipasadak to 2015 a miheca saka 12 a folad saka 26 a romi'ad 9:00 dadaya. Mianingaya a patingso Sra: Ciyang Cen kai Mayaw: Liyang Ci woy Nayaw: Cian Yi tung Pi'arawan to lakaw
